    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban drinks manufacturers from tethering plastic caps to plastic bottles",
        "additional_details": "It currently makes opening and using the bottle difficult for many people, especially the elderly and vulnerable people with limited dexterity.",
        "background": "Pass a law to ban drinks manufacturers from tethering plastic caps to plastic bottles. Return to having plastic caps unattached, separate and fully removable from all plastic bottles. I believe this will make plastic caps on plastic bottles more easily removable for elderly and vulnerable people.",
